{"tid":2408675,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"消遣政客 - 顏純鈎","createTime":"2021-02-15T07:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T08:43:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"339e644a966159793f10254c3a0347071266633a","tid":2408675,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:23:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210215/ECNB5R256NE6PPTJJA467JS6BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210215%2FECNB5R256NE6PPTJJA467JS6BA%2F&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eX0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=e32fec9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210215%2FECNB5R256NE6PPTJJA467JS6BA%2F&h=1141716f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210215/ECNB5R256NE6PPTJJA467JS6BA/</a><br />\n<br />\n消遣政客 - 顏純鈎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KGIe-EB4G1y34hQPc_fR2_RE5oY=/854x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BRMTTXYPB5F6PDCNKQWL2VI34E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKGIe-EB4G1y34hQPc_fR2_RE5oY%3D%2F854x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBRMTTXYPB5F6PDCNKQWL2VI34E.jpg&h=cc831b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《博恩夜夜秀》截圖<br />\n<br />\n台灣有一個電視節目叫「博恩夜夜秀」，主持人很年輕，現場觀眾也以年輕人為主，我看過宋楚瑜和韓國瑜上他節目的視頻。<br />\n<br />\n節目主旨是諷刺時弊，政治經濟民生文化，話題不限，只以調侃譏諷為主調。主持人口齒伶俐，轉數很快，語氣抵死，很受年輕人歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n宋楚瑜和韓國瑜都是台灣老資格政。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政客上娛樂節目，這是台灣才有的。。。。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜還好一點，宋楚瑜從來道貌岸<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n為了爭取選票，政客們。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有得揀先至係老闆，台灣選民有得揀，他們才是台灣的主人。選民要誰上台，誰才能上台，能不能上台取決於選民喜不喜歡你。這是台灣民主制度的一道風景線，也是台灣令人喜愛的一個理由。<br />\n<br />\n近日梁振英和曾鈺成為爭論未來特首是協商好還是選舉好，吵得火紅火綠，其實揀邊。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n先讓我們消遣一下，然。。。。。。"},{"pid":"3207a362390b96ef4893920ccf58c6c2c833de59","tid":2408675,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"佢講錯，政客上娛樂節目唔係台灣獨有，美國都有"}]}